			    <HR color=#000000 SIZE=-1>
			  	there is a roll-back to the last turn on server crashes.<br />
<br />
the game doesn't for the most part save memory-data in database in real-time because otherwise it'd be REALLY inefficient and there would be tons of lag. it saves most stuff each turn into the disk database.<br />
<br />
so if the server crashes it reloads and gets data from the database on disk, but it won't have the current turn, just the last turn and such.<br />
<br />
if i didn't explain that right, apologies, i'm tired. but it isn't a bug =).<br />
<br />
now the server crashing IS a bug, but i don't believe you caused it =)			   <P align=right></P>
